item.title: Green Dip
item.description: Green Dip Ingredients Half a bunch fresh cilantro 1/3 cup mayonnaise 1/4 cup ranch dressing Half an avocado Couple turns freshly ground pepper 1 tbsp onion powder 1 tbsp garlic powder Juice of half a lime Olive oil Instructions Wash and roughly tear cilantro into blender.
